summary: Vampire Save Game, you start as a Female Vampire under College of Winterhold bridge
descriptionHtml:
A Save Game that starts you off as a vampire with some cool items, you \'spawn\' under the Winterhold bridge, as a vampire so, if you go into a village everyone that see\'s you will attack you, if you dont want everyone to attack you, wait until its dark, take the headpiece off and sneak to someone thats in their bed, press E while sneaking and choose Feed, this will revert you to the first stage of vampire, wait 24hours to go to the next level and so on. enjoy! :)

Stats: 100 in everything
All Perks
Deadric Weapons

So.... this IS a god character
